Power BI is more than a tool — it’s a **game-changer** for analysts and businesses. By mastering **data cleaning, DAX, and dashboard design**, you can:

- Turn messy data into clear insights.
- Build interactive dashboards that tell compelling stories.
- Drive measurable business impact.

**Remember:**
> *"Data doesn’t lie, but it doesn’t speak for itself. It is upto an analyst is to give it voice."*











